  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fruity Rogue is a fast paced top-down twin-stick roguelike about fruits. Explore biomes in a series of procedural encounter rooms and challenging boss fights on your way to defeating the evil dragonfruit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>GET FRUITY ITEMS</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exchange health, coins and malus for fruit items in fast paced gameplay. Find the right balance of greed as you try, die, repeat and progress through the floors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.mp4?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>KILL FRUITY ENEMIES</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play unique characters each with run-changing passives and active skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/b12b8dada4f37615ce2ba150d5fa4554.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/b12b8dada4f37615ce2ba150d5fa4554.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>GET FUNKY WEAPONS</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip weapons that utilize stats in different ways, completely changing playstyles and gameplan from run to run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/058785f7ac67dea7a012cea651d780b8.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/058785f7ac67dea7a012cea651d780b8.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>SPEEDRUN THE CHAOS</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fruity Rogue is the freaky child of binding of isaac and nuclear throne with some speedrunning tools added. Stack items, potions, stat multipliers and familiars to reach ultra duper super game breaking-synergies and speedrun your way to the end.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fruity Rogue is a fast paced top-down twin-stick roguelike about fruits. Explore biomes in a series of procedural encounter rooms and challenging boss fights on your way to defeating the evil dragonfruit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>GET FRUITY ITEMS</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exchange health, coins and malus for fruit items in fast paced gameplay. Find the right balance of greed as you try, die, repeat and progress through the floors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/0d309d008ebf7b5d4067e4846ddf293f.mp4?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>KILL FRUITY ENEMIES</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play unique characters each with run-changing passives and active skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/b12b8dada4f37615ce2ba150d5fa4554.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/b12b8dada4f37615ce2ba150d5fa4554.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>GET FUNKY WEAPONS</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip weapons that utilize stats in different ways, completely changing playstyles and gameplan from run to run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/058785f7ac67dea7a012cea651d780b8.poster.avif?t=1763085268\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221570/extras/058785f7ac67dea7a012cea651d780b8.webm?t=1763085268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>SPEEDRUN THE CHAOS</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fruity Rogue is the freaky child of binding of isaac and nuclear throne with some speedrunning tools added. Stack items, potions, stat multipliers and familiars to reach ultra duper super game breaking-synergies and speedrun your way to the end.</p>",
